OL,3,CSNP minister resigns in wake of
OL,4,Cscandal over iPad data roaming charges
OL,6,FMichael Matheson has quit as health
OL,7,Fsecretary, saying he was leaving the
OL,8,Fpost so the row over his iPad roaming
OL,9,Fcharges "does not become a
OL,10,Fdistraction" to the government.
OL,12,FMr Matheson had been under fire since
OL,13,FNovember last year when details of an
OL,14,F#11,000 bill on his Holyrood-issued
OL,15,FiPad were made public.
OL,17,FIn an emotional statement to MSPs, he
OL,18,Frevealed his teenage sons had been
OL,19,Fusing the device as a hotspot so they
OL,20,Fcould watch football while on a family
OL,21,Fholiday to Morocco.
