OL,6,FThe then-health secretary, however,
OL,7,Fhad originally insisted the charges
OL,8,Fhad been run up while he was using it
OL,9,Ffor constituency work during the break.
OL,11,FWhen he learned of his children's use
OL,12,Fof the device, Mr Matheson paid back
OL,13,Fthe charges, which had originally been
OL,14,Fpicked up by the Scottish Parliament.
OL,16,FWith the Scottish Parliament Corporate
OL,17,FBody conducting an investigation, Mr
OL,18,FMatheson said he was "conscious that
OL,19,Fthis process will conclude in the
OL,20,Fcoming weeks".
