OL,6,FIn a letter to First Minister Humza
OL,7,FYousaf, he said: "I have still not
OL,8,Freceived the findings of their review,
OL,9,Fhowever, it is in the best interests
OL,10,Fof myself and the government for me
OL,11,Fnow to step down to ensure that this
OL,12,Fdoes not become a distraction to
OL,13,Ftaking forward the government's
OL,14,Fagenda."
